        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer184254200" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5366109931495649970">Oh Lucinda Price. Could you <i>be</i> any stupider?<br/><br/><img src='https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1380353025ra/706427.gif' height='250' width='400' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/></span>
  <span id="freeText5366109931495649970" style="display:none">Oh Lucinda Price. Could you <i>be</i> any stupider?<br><br><img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1380353025ra/706427.gif" height="250" width="400" class="gr-hostedUserImg"></span>
