<div id="review_2156726734" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2156726734" />
    <a title="Alaina" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/50620706-alaina"><img alt="Alaina" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1451325817p2/50620706.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2156726734?book_show_action=true">Oct 18, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Alaina" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Alaina" href="/user/show/50620706-alaina">Alaina</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="did not like it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">did not like it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/50620706-alaina?shelf=fantasy">fantasy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/50620706-alaina?shelf=mystery">mystery</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/50620706-alaina?shelf=2017">2017</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/50620706-alaina?shelf=young-adult">young-adult</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/50620706-alaina?shelf=paranormal">paranormal</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/50620706-alaina?shelf=supernatural">supernatural</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/50620706-alaina?shelf=fiction">fiction</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2156726734" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5631096142645628573">I couldn&apos;t remember if I liked the first book <i>Fallen</i> or not and since I said I was going to do a buddy read for this book, <i>Torment</i>, I just sort of went with it. I was also way too lazy to look up my review/rating for Fallen. Plus, it honestly doesn&apos;t really matter to me how I felt about the first book - what matters if how I felt about this book.<br/><br/><b>I hated it.</b><br/><br/>I hated it so fucking much. I would rather sit in the dentist office for like 48 hours than read this book ever again. <i>Side note: I have perf</i></span>
  <span id="freeText5631096142645628573" style="display:none">I couldn't remember if I liked the first book <i>Fallen</i> or not and since I said I was going to do a buddy read for this book, <i>Torment</i>, I just sort of went with it. I was also way too lazy to look up my review/rating for Fallen. Plus, it honestly doesn't really matter to me how I felt about the first book - what matters if how I felt about this book.<br /><br /><b>I hated it.</b><br /><br />I hated it so fucking much. I would rather sit in the dentist office for like 48 hours than read this book ever again. <i>Side note: I have perfectly healthy teeth (very straight and everything) and no cavities either. I just hate the dentist and the scraping they do during the cleaning. It makes me cringe.</i><br /><br />If I hated someone so much I would probably send them this book.<br /><br />I don't even want to dive into <i>Torment</i> or hide/tell you spoilers about this book. Nope, not one ounce of me wants to do that at all. I'll just complain about how annoying the characters were. It was such a boring read that I would put down this book all of the time and do something else. Like, read another book (or four), do laundry, shower, walk the dogs, etc. I would rather watch a show that I hate than read this book. <br /><br />I apologize to anyone that actually liked this book and then I also have to ask - DID WE READ THE SAME BOOK?!?<br /><br />I'm done with this series. I will not be picking up the next book. I will never reread this series ever again. I'd rather eat dog shit.</span>
